    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="958419146">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-958419146" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-958419146" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="958419146">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/73714750/">妖怪瓶</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">新闻写作或者说媒体写作的方式写历史，倒不必苛求全面和深度，重要的其实是细节的描摹和挖掘，这点是其他写作方式不可替代的。细节带来了可读性和代入感。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
